@baseUrl = http://localhost:3555
@gateway = https://api-gateway-ashy-seven.vercel.app
@consumerId = 67be4156-dee8-4c36-a205-61756c77c926

### Extrato Cashback — Direto na API (local)
### Retorna: { balance: { balance, description }, transactions: [...] }
GET {{baseUrl}}/extrato/{{consumerId}}
Accept: application/json

### Extrato Cashback — Via API Gateway (produção)
GET {{gateway}}/api/cashback/extrato/{{consumerId}}
Accept: application/json
